                  "source": "## How it fits together\n\nEach leaf — heading, markdown, image — is a non-positional content type, so the grammar requires it to be wrapped in a `block`. The block applies per-block concerns (title, visibility, theme) to the single leaf it carries.\n\nBecause the same interpolation pass runs over every leaf, the product name **Lattice** and version **0.3.0** appear identically wherever they are referenced."
